<p>Friday 29.3.18. went over for ride&nbsp; had a fall from &quot;Mickie&quot; who has broken both knees.</p>
<p>Saturday 30/3/18. went around lines with Martin who hasn&#39;t improved much</p>
<p>Sunday 31/3/18&nbsp; went for walk around Neuve Eglise, making all arrangements for shift</p>
<p>Monday 1/4/18&nbsp; Went for a ride &amp; had a glass of wine with Little at &quot;Ye Olde Kicking Mule&quot;</p>
<p>Tuesday 2/4/18&nbsp; moved to Aldershot Camp- Bn relieved in line by South Lancashires</p>
